media:group.media:title: Donkey Kong’s Most Creepy Mystery
media:group.media:description:
Today we dive into the mystery behind some strange backgrounds of an obscure Donkey Kong 3 port for Japanese PC's. Why were they made like this? Do they have any significance? Let's find out together!

More info about the game here: https://www.mariowiki.com/Donkey_Kong_3:_Dai_Gyakush%C5%AB
